### ğŸ“Š Financial Summary
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|:-------|:----------|:------------|
| `GET` | `/api/summary/` | Returns balance, total income, total expenses, and totals per category |

**Example Response:**
```json
{
  "balance": 2964.10,
  "income": 3000.0,
  "expenses": 35.9,
  "by_category": [
    {"category": "Salary", "total": 3000.0},
    {"category": "Food", "total": 35.9}
  ]
}
